5|$|Mgr. Libor Michálek, MPA (born 1968) is a Czech economist, politician, and <b>whistleblower.</b> He led {{successful}} corruption {{cases against}} the Czech National Property Fund and the Environment Ministry as former employees of both. He {{is the first}} Pirate Party candidate to be elected to office in a national legislature. His senatorial term is 2012–2018.|$|E
